 guitar, on a long run, or with the head buried in a book. Or wishing there was a guitar around.<\/em><\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author\"><figure class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__avatar\"><img class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__avatar-img\" src=\"http:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/daria_circle.jpg\" alt=\"Daria Gangardt\"\/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__content\"><span class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__name\">Daria Gangardt<\/span><p class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__biography\">PhD student.<br\/><em>Rider of (gravitational) waves, fencing fanatic, binge-watcher extraordinaire. Fan of trying new things and exploring new places<\/em>.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author\"><figure class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__avatar\"><img class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__avatar-img\" src=\"http:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/viola.jpeg\" alt=\"Viola De Renzis\"\/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__content\"><span class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__name\">Viola De Renzis<\/span><p class=\"wp-block-coblocks-author__biography\">PhD student.<br\/><em>Music addicted, guitar player (or at least I try), nature lover and manga reader. I&#8217;m intrigued by the questions we cannot answer and that&#8217;s where my passion for astrophysics and black holes comes from.<\/em><\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Some<strong> group pictures<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow aligncenter\" data-effect=\"slide\"><div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_container swiper-container\"><ul class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_swiper-wrapper swiper-wrapper\"><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2124